{"tid":2026975,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾為777站台TVB女記者 被指冒認「東方星島」後逃入立會保安室","createTime":"2020-05-21T09:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T10:58:28.000Z","uid":321059,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3ca85a8dc7cf08675686e8ae8660b0d3ddf91d1","tid":2026975,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:18:05.000Z","msg":"做TVB記者，唔係好多人夢想咩？今日教育界議員葉建源喺立法會講述教協嘅問卷調查結果時，突然有女記者問佢對教協被指喺旺角同銅鑼灣會址有僭建有何回應？<span style=\"color: red;\">當葉Sir問佢係嚟自邊間媒體時，女記即有啲口窒咁答：「東方星島」</span>，但兩報記者都未見過呢位「同事」。有《東方》記者事後查詢該女記嚟自邊個傳媒，問佢點解要冒認《東方》同《星島》時？女記無表明身份，只話：「我無冒認啊！我只係睇到佢哋嘅報道」，繼而喺立法會走廊拔足狂奔落扶手電梯，其間一直拒絕表明係邊間傳媒記者，再掩面大嗌：「唔好意思！我可唔可以求救？」，之後衝咗入平日只准立法會保安進入嘅保安室。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n八方發現，呢位叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">章詠欣</span></span>嘅大台女記者「大有來頭」，過去除咗曾任港大學生會國事學會第45屆幹事會主席，更曾於2017年喺林鄭參選特首嘅競選分享大會，企正喺林鄭隔離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200521/LXR2INABH6ORA2ZHS7MWVBZGJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200521%2FLXR2INABH6ORA2ZHS7MWVBZGJ4%2F&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsYV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=c2608308\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200521%2FLXR2INABH6ORA2ZHS7MWVBZGJ4%2F&h=4f083631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200521/LXR2INABH6ORA2ZHS7MWVBZGJ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">CCTVB 已經無哂良心記者</span></span>"},{"pid":"63d8a0b29646f798df57ba7577f80826f6a4cc49","tid":2026975,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有自知之明<br />\n知TVB黑人憎"},{"pid":"f51c60b910d3d4508cd483e5929038a2c9a34ef7","tid":2026975,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:05:20.000Z","msg":"100％共諜嚟"},{"pid":"e37f5eb1b4c126c4d39fb48b0995cf68a166e